hadiths[148]{hadithnumber,text}:
1,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' namaz baghair wuzu key qubul nahin ki jati padhi. aur na sadqa haram maal sey qubul kya jata hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein ye hadees sab sey sahih aur Hasan hai padhi. . padhi. 2- is bab mein abul-Maleeh key walid Usama Abu-Hurera aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain.
2,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jab musalman ya momin banda wuzu karta aur apna chehra dhota hai to pani key sath ya pani key aakhiri qatrey key sath uskey chehrey sey wo tamam gunah jhad jatey hain padhi. , jo uski aakhon ney kiye they ya isi tarah ki koi aur baat farmaai , phir jab wo apney haathon ko dhota hai to pani key sath ya pani key aakhiri qatrey key sath wo tamam gunah jhad jatey hain jo uskey haathon sey huye hain, yahan tak ke wo gunahon sey pak o saaf ho kar nikalta hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai padhi. , padhi. 2- is bab mein Usman bin Affaan, Soban, Sunabihi , Amr bin Abasa , Salman aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. . Sunabihi jinhoney abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai, unka samaa, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey nahin hai, unka naam Abdur-Rehman bin aseela , aur kunniyat abu-Adbullah hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key paas safar kya, raastey hi mein they ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka intiqal ho gaya, unhoney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey mutaaddid ahadees riwayat ki hain. aur Sunabih bin Aasara Himsi Sabab Rasool hain, in ko Sunabihi bhi kaha jata hai, unhi ki hadees hai ke mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ''main tumharey zariey sey dusri ummaton main apni aksariyat par fakhr karunga to merey baad tum hergiz eik doosrey ko qatl na karna ''."
3,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' namaz ki kunji wuzu hai, aur uska tahreema sirf (Allah akbar) kehna hai padhi. aur namaz mein jo cheezen haram thin wo (Assalamualaikum Warahmatullah) kehney hi sey halal hoti hain'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein ye hadees sab sey sahih aur Hasan hai, 2- Abdullah bin Muhammad bin Aqeel Sadooq hain padhi. , baaz ehle-ilm ney unkey hafizey key talluq sey un par kalam kya hai, mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko ye kehtey huye suna ke Ahmed bin Hanbal , Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya aur Humedi : Abdullah bin Muhammad bin Aqeel ki riwayat sey hujjat pakadtey they, aur wo maqaribul hadees hain, 4- is bab mein Jabir aur abu Saeed khudri Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
4,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' namaz jannat ki kunji hai, aur namaz ki kunji wuzu hai ''."
5,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab qazaey-hajat key liye pakhana mein dakhil hotey to ye dua padhtey : اللهم أعوذ بك من الخبث أو الخبث والخبائث  aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun napaki sey aur napak shakhs sey , ya napak jinon sey aur napak Jinniyon sey '' padhi. . Shoba kehtey hain : abdul-Azeez ney dusri baar « اللهم إني أعوذ بك » key bajaey «أعوذبا الله» kaha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali , Zaid bin Arqam , Jabir aur ibne-Masood (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is baab mein sab sey sahih aur umda hai, Zaid bin Arqam ki sanad mein iztirab hai, Imam Bukhari kehtey hain : ke ho sakta hai Qatada ney isey ( Zaid bin Arqam sey aur Nazar bin Anas an Abiiya) dono sey eik sath riwayat kya ho."
6,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab qazaey-hajat key liye bait الخلاء mein dakhil hotey to padhtey : اللهم أعوذ بك من الخبث أو الخبث والخبائث ''aey Allah main teri panah chahta hun napak jinon aur napak Jinniyon sey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
7,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat key baad jab pakhana sey nikaltey to farmatey : « غفرانك‏ » yani '' aey Allah : main teri bakhshish ka talabgar hun '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai padhi. , padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) hi ki hadees maroof hai."
8,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jab tum qazaey-hajat key liye jaao to pakhana ya peshab key waqt qibley ki taraf munh na karo aur na peeth , balke munh ko purab ya pashchim ki taraf karo '' padhi. . abu-Ayyub Ansari kehtey hain : hum Sham aaye to hamney dekha ke pakhaney qibla rukh banaey gaey hain to qibley ki samt sey tirchhey mud jatey aur hum Allah sey maghfirat talab kartey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz Zubaidi , Maaqil bin abi Haisham ( Maaqil bin abi Maaqil ( abu-Umama , Abu-Hurera aur Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. - abu-Ayyub ki hadees is baab mein sab sey umda aur sab sey sahih hai, padhi. - abul-Waleed makki kehtey hain : abu-Adbullah Muhammad bin Idrees Shafai ka kehna hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney jo ye farmaya hai ke pakhana ya peshab key waqt qibley ki taraf munh na karo aur na peeth , us sey murad sirf Sehra ( maidan ( mein na karna hai, rahey baney banaey pakhana-ghar, to un mein qibley ki taraf munh karna jayez hai, isi tarah Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya ney bhi kaha hai, Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey pakhana ya peshab key waqt qibley ki taraf sirf peeth karney ki rukhsat hai, raha qibley ki taraf munh karna to ye kisi bhi tarah jayez nahin, goya ke) Imam Ahmed ( qibley ki taraf munh karney ko na Sehra mein jayez qarar detey hain aur na hi baney banaey pakhana-ghar mein) albatta peeth karney ko baitul-Khala mein jayez samajhtey hain ( ."
9,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya ke hum peshab key waqt qibley ki taraf munh karen, phir mainey wafat sey eik saal pehley aap ko qibley ki taraf munh kar key peshab kartey huye dekha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Qatada , Aaisha , aur Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
10,"abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko qibley ki taraf munh kar key peshab kartey huye dekha hai. Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey ye hadees ibne-Lahiaa ki hadees ( jis mein Jabir key baad abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ka wasta hai) sey ziyada sahih hai, ibne-Lahiaa Muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain, Yahya bin Saeed Qattan waghera ney un ki hifz key aetbar sey tazeef ki hai."
11,eik roz main ( apni behan ( Hafsa (Raziallahu Anha) key ghar ki chhat par chadha to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap Sham ki taraf munh aur Kaba ki taraf peeth kar key qazaey-hajat farma rahey hain padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
12,"jo tum sey ye kahey ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho kar peshab kartey they to tum uski tasdeeq na karna , aap beth kar hi peshab kartey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein umr , Barida , Abdur-Rehman bin Hasna (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki ye hadees sab sey ziyada umda aur sahih hai, padhi. - umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees mein hai ke mujhey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney khadey ho kar peshab kartey huye dekha to farmaya : '' umr ! khadey ho kar peshab na karo '' , chunanche uskey baad sey mainey kabhi bhi khadey ho kar peshab nahin kya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki is hadees ko Abdul-Karim ibne-Abi al-Makhariq ney marfooan riwayat kya hai aur wo muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain, Ayub sakhtiyaan ney un ki tazeef ki hai aur un par kalam kya hai, neez ye hadees Ubedullah ney Nafey sey aur Nafey ney ibne-Umar sey ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke mainey jab sey Islam qubul kya kabhi khadey ho kar peshab nahin kya. ye hadees Abdul-Karim bin abi al-Makhariq ki hadees sey) riwayat key aetbar sey) ziyada sahih hai padhi. , 2- is bab mein Barida (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees mehfooz nahin hai, khadey ho kar peshab karney ki mumaaniat adab key aetbar sey hai haram nahin hai, Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke tum khadey ho kar peshab karo ye phoohadpan hai."
13,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar eik qom key kudey-karkat key dher par sey huwa to aap ney is par khadey ho kar peshab kya, mein aap key liye wuzu ka pani laya , usey rakh kar mein peechey hatney laga , to aap ney mujhey isharay sey bulaya , main ( aa kar) aap ki ediyon key paas khada ho gaya, aap ney wuzu kya aur apney mozon par masah kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Wakee kehtey hain : ye hadees masah key silsiley mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey marvi hadeeson mein sab sey ziyada sahih hai. padhi. - ye hadees ba-riwayat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey marvi hai padhi. abu-Waeil ki hadees jisey unhoney Huzefa sey riwayat kya ( Mughira ki riwayat sey) ziyada sahih hai padhi. , padhi. - muhaddeseen mein sey ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney khadey ho kar peshab karney ki ijazat di hai."
14,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab qazaey-hajat ka irada farmatey to jab tak zamin sey bilkul qarib na ho jatey apney kapdey nahin uthatey they. dusri sanad mein Aamash sey riwayat hai, ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab qazaey-hajat ka irada farmatey kapdey jab tak zamin sey qarib nahin ho jatey nahin uthatey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye dono ahadees mursal hain, isliye ke kaha jata hai : dono ahadees key Raavi Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Mehran al-Aamash ney na hi to Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey sama'at ki hai aur na hi kisi aur Sabab sey , sirf itna hai ke Anas ko sirf unhoney dekha hai, Aamash kehtey hain ke mainey unhen namaz padhtey dekha hai phir un ki namaz ki keyfiyat bayan ki."
15,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya hai ke aadmi apney dahiney haath sey apna zakar (uzue-tanasul) chhuey padhi. . is baab mein Aaisha , Salman , Abu-Hurera aur Sehal-bin-Haneef (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. - aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, un logon ney dahiney haath sey istinja karney ko makrooh jana hai."
16,"Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) sey bator tanz ye baat kahi gaee ke tumharey Nabi ney tumhen sari cheezen sikhai hain yahan tak key peshab pakhana karna bhi, to Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) ney bator fakhr kaha : haan , aisa hi hai hamarey Nabi ney hamen peshab pakhana key waqt qibley ki taraf munh karney , dahiney haath sey istinja karney , aur teen pathar sey kam sey istinja karney , aur gobar aur haddi sey istinja karney sey hamen mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Aaisha , Khuzaima bin Sabit Jabir aur khallad bin Sayib (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. - Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is baab mein Hasan sahih hai, padhi. - Sahaba o Tabe-een mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai ke pathar sey istinja kar lena kafi hai jab wo pakhana aur peshab key asar ko zaayel o pak kar dey agar-che pani sey istinja na kya gaya ho, yehi qol Sory, ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi hai."
17,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat key liye nikley to aap ney farmaya : '' merey liye teen pathar dhoond laao '' , main do pathar aur eik gobar ka tukda ley kar aap ki khidmat mein aaya to aap ney dono patharon ko ley liya aur gobar key tukdey ko phenk diya aur farmaya : '' ye napak hai'' padhi. .) Abu-Is'haq Sabeei Suqa aur mudallis Raavi hain, budhapey mein hafizey mein ikhtilaat ho gaya tha isliye jin riwayaton ney un sey ikhtilaat sey pehley suna un ki riwayat maqbool hai, aur jin logon ney ikhtilaat key baad suna un ki riwayat zaeef , ye hadees Abu-Is'haq sey unkey talaamiza ney mukhtalif andaz sey riwayat ki hai) . Imam Tirmizi ney yahan : ibne-Masood ki is hadees ko sanad key sath « Israel an abi Is-haq an abi Ubeda an ibne-Masood » riwayat karney key baad Israel ki mutaabiat padhi. mein Qais bin Rabee ki riwayat ka zikr kya hai, phir sanad key sath« Mamar o Ammar bin Ruzeq an abi Is-haq an Alqama an ibne-Masood » ki riwayat zikr ki hai, phir sanad key sath « Zakariya bin abi zyada o zuhair an abi Is-haq an Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed an Aswad bin Yazeed an Abdullah bin Masood » riwayat zikr ki aur farmaya ke is hadees mein iztirab hai, neez Israel ki riwayat ko sahih tareen qarar diya, ye bhi wazeh kya ke abu Ubeda ka samaa, apney walid ibne-Masood sey nahin hai phir wazeh kya ke zuhair ney is hadees ko basanad « Abu-Is'haq an Abdur-Rehman bin-Aswad an Abi an Abdullah bin Masood » riwayat kya hai, to un Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney apni sahih mein us ko jagah dey kar apni tarjeeh ka zikr kar diya hai, jabke Tirmizi ka istidlaal ye hai ke «Israel o Qais an abi Is-haq » ziyada sahih riwayat isliye hai ke Israel abu-Is-haq ki hadees key ziyada Hafiz o muttaqin hain, Qais ney bhi Israel ki mutaabiat ki hai, aur wazeh rahey ke zuhair ney abu-Is-haaq sey aakhir mein ikhtilaat key baad suna hai, isliye unki riwayat Israel ki riwayat key muqabley mein qawi nahin hai."
18,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' gobar aur haddi sey istinja na karo kyonkey wo tumharey bhaiyon jinon ki khurak hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abu-Hurera , Salman , Jabir , ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees marvi hain. padhi. - Ismail bin Ibrahim waghera ney basanad « Dawud ibne-Abi Hind an Shaaby an Alqama » riwayat ki hai ke Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) « لیلة الجن » mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key sath they padhi. aagey unhoney puri hadees zikr ki jo lambi hai, Shaaby kehtey hain ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya gobar aur haddi sey istinja na karo kyonkey ye tumharey bhaiyon ( jinon ( ki khurak hai, padhi. - goya Ismail bin Ibrahim ki riwayat Hafs bin Ghiyas ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai padhi. , 3- ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai, - aur is baab mein Jabir aur ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
19,"tum aurten apney shohron sey kaho ke wo pani sey istinja kya karen, main un sey) ye baat kehtey ( sharma rahi hun, kyonkey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aisa hi kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jareer bin Abdullah bijli , Anas , aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. - isi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai padhi. , wo pani sey istinja karney ko pasand kartey hain agar-che pathar sey istinja unkey nazdik kafi hai phir bhi pani sey istinja ko unhoney mustahab aur afzal qarar diya hai. sufiyan Sory, ibne-Mubarak, Shafai , Ahmed , Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi key qaail hain."
20,"mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key sath eik safar mein tha, aap qazaey-hajat key liye nikley to bahut door nikal gaey padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdur-Rehman bin abi Qurad , abu-Qatada , Jabir , Yahya bin Ubaid an Abiy , abu Musa , ibne-Abbas aur Bilal bin Haris (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. - riwayat ki jati hai ke neez Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) peshab key liye is tarah jagah dhoondtey they jis tarah musafir utarney key liye jagah dhoondta hai. - abu-Salma ka naam Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman bin Auf Zohri hai."
21,"Abdullah bin Mughaffal (rz) kehtey hain ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya hai ke aadmi apney ghusl khaney mein peshab karey aur farmaya : '' ziyada tar waswasey usi sey paida hotey hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab main eik aur Sabab sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Ash-as bin Abdullah ki riwayat sey marfoo jantey hain, unhen Ash-as Aama bhi kaha jata hai, 3- ehle-ilm mein sey kuch logon ney ghusl khaney mein peshab karney ko makrooh qarar diya hai, in logon ka kehna hai ke ziyada tar waswasey isi sey janm letey hain, 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney iski rukhsat di hai jin mein sey ibn sirin bhi hain, ibn sirin sey kaha gaya : kaha jata hai ke aksar waswasey usi sey janm letey hain? to unhoney jawab diya ke hamara rab Allah hai, uska koi shareek nahin, Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain ke ghusl khaney mein peshab karney ko jayez qarar diya gaya hai, b-sharte-ke is mein sey pani beh jata ho"
22,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' agar mujhey apni ummat ko harj aur mashaqqat mein mubtala karney ka khatra na hota to main unhen har namaz key waqt miswak karney ka hukm deta '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ba-riwayat abu-Salma , Abu-Hurera aur Zaid bin Khalid Raziallahu anhuma ki marvi dono hadisein merey nazdik sahih hain, Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ka khayal hai ke abu-Salma ki Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hadees ziyada sahih hai padhi. , padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq , Ali , Aaisha , ibne-Abbas , Huzefa , Zaid bin Khalid , Anas , Abdullah bin Amr , ibne-Umar , Umme-Habiba , abu-Umama , abu-Ayyub , Tammam bin Abbas , Abdullah bin Hanzala , Umme-Salma , Waasila al-Asqa aur abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
23,"mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huye suna hai : '' agar mujhey apni ummat ko harj o mashaqqat mein mubtala karney ka khatra na hota to main unhen har salaat key waqt (wujuban) miswak karney ka hukm deta, neez main Isha ko tihai raat tak muakhkhar karta (Raavi hadees) abu-Salma kehtey hain : isliye Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) namaz key liye masjid aatey to miswak unkey kaan par bilkul isi tarah hoti jaisey kaatib key kaan par qalam hota hai, wo namaz key liye khadey hotey to miswak kartey phir usey uski jagah par wapis rakh letey padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
24,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi raat ko neend sey uthey to apna haath bartan padhi. mein na daley jab tak ke is par do ya teen baar pani na dal ley , kyonkey wo nahin janta ke uska haath raat mein kahan kahan raha hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein ibne-Umar, Jabir aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 3- Shafai kehtey hain : main har so kar uthney waley key liye, chahey wo dopahar mein qailula kar key utha ho ya kisi aur waqt mein 4- pasand karta hun ke wo jab tak apna haath na dhoey usey wuzu key pani mein na daley aur agar usney dhoney sey pehley haath dal diya to main uskey us amal ko makrooh samajhta hun lekin us sey pani faasid nahin hoga b-sharte-ke uskey haath mein koi gandagi na lagi ho, Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : jab koi raat ko jaagey aur dhoney sey pehley pani mein haath dal dey to us pani ko merey nazdik baha dena behtar hai, Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : jab wo raat ya din kisi bhi waqt neend sey jaagey to apna haath wuzu key pani mein na daley jab tak ke usey dho na ley۔"
25,"mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo « Bismillah » kar key wuzu shuru na karey uska wuzu nahin hota padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Aaisha , Abu-Hurera , abu Saeed Khudri , Sehal bin Saad aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : mujhey is baab mein koi aisi hadees nahin malum jiski sanad umda ho, 3- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : agar koi qasdan «Bismillah» kehna chhod dey to wo dobara wuzu karey aur agar bhool kar chhodey ya wo is hadees ki taaweel kar raha ho to ye usey kafi ho jaeyga, 4- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke is baab mein sab sey achi yehi mazkura baala hadees Ribah bin Abdur-Rehman ki hai, yani Saeed bin Zaid bin Amr bin Nafeel ki hadees۔"
26,Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey ooper wali hadees key misl marvi hai.
27,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jab tum wuzu karo to naak jhaado aur jab dheley sey istinja karo to taaq dheley lo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Usman , laqeet bin Sabra , ibne-Abbas , Miqdam bin Maadikarb , Wayl bin Hajar aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- Salma bin Qais wali hadees Hasan sahih hai, 3- jo kulli na karey aur naak mein pani na chadhaey uskey barey mein ehle-ilm mein ikhtilaf hai : eik giroh ka kehna hai ke jab koi un dono chizon ko wuzu mein chhod dey aur namaz padh ley to wo namaz ko lotaye padhi. un logon ki raey hai ke wuzu aur janabat dono mein ye hukm barabar hai, ibne-Abi Leila , Abdullah bin Mubarak , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya yehi kehtey hain, Imam Ahmed ( mazeed ( kehtey hain ke naak mein pani chadhana kulli karney sey ziyada taakidi hukm hai, aur ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat kehti hai ke janabat mein kulli na karney aur naak na jhaadney ki surat mein namaz lotaye aur wuzu mein na lotaye padhi. ye Sufiyan Sory aur baaz ehle-koofa ka qol hai, eik giroh ka kehna hai ke na wuzu mein lotaye aur na janabat mein kyonkey ye dono cheezen masnoon hain, to jo unhen wuzu aur janabat mein chhod dey is par namaz lautana wajib nahin, ye Malik aur Shafai ka aakhiri qol hai."
28,"mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney eik hi chullu sey kulli ki aur naak mein pani dala , teen baar aap ney aisa kya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- Abdullah bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma ki ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 3- Malik, Sufiyan , ibn Uena aur deegar kaee logon ney ye hadees Amr bin Yahya sey riwayat ki hai. lekin un logon ney ye baat zikr nahin ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney eik hi chullu sey kulli ki aur naak mein pani dala , usey sirf Khalid hi ney zikr kya hai aur Khalid muhaddeseen key nazdik Suqa aur Hafiz hain. baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha hai ke eik hi chullu sey kulli karna aur naak mein pani dalna kafi hoga, aur baaz ney kaha hai ke dono key liye alag-alag pani lena hamen ziyada pasand hai, Shafai kehtey hain ke agar un dono ko eik hi chalo mein jama karey to jayez hai lekin agar alag alag chullu sey karey to ye hamen ziyada pasand hai."
29,mainey Ammar bin Yasir Raziallahu anhuma ko dekha ke unhoney wuzu kya to apni dadhi mein Khilal kya padhi. un sey kaha gaya ya Raavi hadees Hassan ney kaha ke mainey un sey kaha : kya aap apni dadhi ka Khilal kar rahey hain? to unhoney jawab diya ke main dadhi ka Khilal kyon na karun jabke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dadhi ka Khilal kartey dekha hai.
30,"Ammar bin Yasir sey ooper hi ki hadees key misl marfooan marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Usman, Aaisha, Umme-Salma, Anas , ibne-Abi Aufi aur abu-Ayyub (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke is baab mein sab sey ziyada sahih hadees Aamir bin Shaqeeq ki hai, jisey unhoney abu-Waeil sey aur abu-Waeil ney Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kya hai) jo aagey aa rahi hai) , 3- Sahaba aur Tabe-een mein sey aksar ehle-ilm usi key qaail hain, un logon ki raey hai ke dadhi ka Khilal (masnoon) hai aur usi key qaail Shafai bhi hain, Ahmed kehtey hain ke agar koi dadhi ka Khilal karna bhool jaey to wuzu jayez hoga, Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke agar koi bhool kar chhod dey ya Khilal wali hadees ki taaweel kar raha ho to usey kafi ho jaeyga aur agar qasdan jaan-bujh kar chhodey to wo usey ( wuzu ko) lotaye."
31,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni dadhi mein Khilal kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
32,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney apney haathon sey sar ka masah kya to unhen aagey sey peechey ley gaey aur peechey sey aagey laye, yani apney sar key agley hissey sey shuru kya phir unhen guddi tak ley gaey phir unhen wapis lotaya yahan tak ke usi jagah wapis ley aaye jahan sey shuru kya tha, phir aap ney dono pair dhoey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Muawiya , Miqdam bin Maadikarb aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees sab sey sahih aur umda hai aur usi key qaail Shafai Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya hain."
33,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney apney sar ka do martaba padhi. masah kya, aap ney ( pehley (apney sar key pichley hissey sey shuru kya padhi. , phir (dusri baar ( uskey agley hissey sey aur apney kanon key andruni aur berooni dono hisson ka masah kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai aur Abdullah bin Zaid ki hadees sanad key aetbar sey us sey ziyada sahih aur ziyada umda hai, 2- ehle-koofa mein sey baaz log usi hadees ki taraf gaey hain, unhi mein sey Wakee bin Jarrah bhi hain padhi. ."
34,"mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wuzu kartey huye dekha , aap ney apney sar ka eik baar masah kiya, agley hissey ka bhi aur pichhley hissey ka bhi aur apni dono kanpatiyon aur kanon ka bhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Rabee (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab (sisile) mein Ali aur Talha bin Musrif bin Amr key dada (Amr bin Kaab Yami) (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain, 3- aur bhi sanadon sey ye baat bayan hui hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney apney sar ka masah eik baar kiya. 4- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai aur Jafar bin Muhammad, Sufiyan Sory, ibne Mubarak, Shafai padhi. Ahmed bin Hanbal aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain. 5- Sufiyan bin Uena kehtey hain ke mainey Jafar bin Muhammad sey sar key masah key barey mein puchha : kya eik martaba sar ka masah kar lena kafi hai? to unhoney kaha : haan qism hai Allah ki."
35,unhoney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney wuzu kiya aur apney dono haathon key bachey huye pani key ilawa naey pani sey apney sar ka masah kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ibne Lahiyaa ney ye hadees sanad ke saath «Hibbaan bin Waasey an Abiy» riwayat ki hai ke Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu kiya aur apney sar ka masah apney dono haathon key bachey huye pani sey kiya. 3- Amr bin Haris ki riwayat jisey unhon-ney Hibban sey riwayat ki hai ziyada sahih hai padhi. kyonkey aur bhi kaee sanadon sey Abdullah bin Zaid waghera sey bayan hui hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney apney sar key masah key liye naya pani liya. 4- aksar ehle-ilm (aalimon) ka amal isi par hai. un ki raey hai ke sar key masah key liye naya pani liya jaey.
36,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney apney sar ka aur apney dono kanon key baalaai (oopri) aur andruni hisson ka masah kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab (silsile) mein Rabee (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- aksar ehle-ilm (aalimon) ka isi par amal hai. in logon ki raey hai ke dono kanon key baalaai (oopri) aur andruni dono hisson ka masah kiya jaey."
37,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu kiya to apna chehra teen baar dhoya aur apney dono haath teen baar dhoey aur apney sar ka masah kiya aur farmaya : ''dono kaan sar mein dakhil hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Quteba ka kehna hai ke Hammad kehtey hain : mujhey nahin malum ke ye Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka qol hai ya Abu-Umama ka. 2- is bab (silsile) mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- is hadees ki sanad qawi nahin hai, 4- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm (aalimon) ka isi par amal hai aur isi key qaail Sufiyan Sory, ibne Mubarak aur Is-haq bin Raahviya hain padhi. aur baaz ehle-ilm (aalimon) ney kaha hai ke kaan key samney ka hissa chehre mein sey hai (isliye isey dhoya jaey) aur peechhey ka hissa sar mein sey hai. (isliye masah kiya jaey) Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke main is baat ko pasand karta hun ke kaan key samney key hissey ka masah chehra key sath keiarey (yani chehre key sath dhoey) aur pichhley hissey ka sar key sath. Shafai kehtey hain ke dono alag-alag sunnat hain (isliye) dono ka masah naey pani sey karey."
38,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''jab tum wuzu karo to ungliyon ka Khilal karo. '' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab (silsile) mein ibne-Abbas, Mustaurid bin Shaddad Fahri aur abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 3- ehle-ilm (aalimon) ka isi par amal hai ke wuzu mein apney pairon ki ungliyon ka khilal karey isi key qaail Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya hain. Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke wuzu mein apney dono haathon aur pairon ki ungliyon ka khilal karey."
39,Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''jab tum wuzu karo to apney haathon aur pairon ki ungliyon key beech khilal karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
40,"mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap wuzu kartey to apney dono pairon ki ungliyon ko apney khinsar (haath ki chhoti ungli) sey maltey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, isey hum sirf ibne Lahiaa key tareeqe hi sey jantey hain."
41,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''ediyon key dhoney mein kotahi baratney walon key liye kharabi hai yani jahannam ki aag hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Umar, Aaisha, Jabir,  Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz Zubaidi Muaiqeeb, Khalid bin waleed, Shurehbil bin Hasana, Amr bin al-Aas aur Yazeed bin abi Sufiyan sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey bayan hui hai ke ''un ediyon aur qadam key talwon key liye jo wuzu mein sookhi reh jaeyn kharabi hai yani jahannam ki aag hai'' is hadees ka matlab ye huwa ke pairon ka masah jayez nahin agar un par mozey ya jurab na hon."
42,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu key ang eik-eik baar dhoey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Umar, Jabir, Barida, abu-Raafea', aur ibne-al-Faka (Raziallauh Anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- ibne-Abbas ki ye hadees is baab mein sab sey umda aur sahih hai. 3- Rushdain bin Saad waghera basand (Suhaak bin Shurehbil an Zaid bin Aslam an Abiy) sey riwayat ki hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : ''nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu key ang ko eik eik baar dhoyaa.''  ye (riwayat) kuchh bhi nahin hai sahih wohi riwayat hai jisey ibne Ajlan, Hisham bin Saad, Sufiyan Sory aur Abdul-Azeez bin Muhammad ney basand (Zaid bin Aslam an Ata bin Yasar an ibne-Abbas an Nabi karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam))  riwayat kiya hai."
43,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu key ang do-do baar dhoey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- hum ye jantey hain ke isey sirf ibne Soban ney Abdullah bin Fazal sey riwayat kiya hai aur ye sanad Hasan sahih hai. 4- Hamaam ney basand (Aamir Al Ahwal an Ata an abi Huraira) riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu key ang teen-teen baar dhoey."
44,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu key ang teen teen baar dhoey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Usman, Aaisha, Rabee, ibne-Umar, abu-Umama, abu-Raafea', Abdullah bin Amr, Muaawiya, abu-Huraira, Jabir, Abdullah bin Zaid aur Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is baab mein sab sey umda aur sahih hai kyonkey ye Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey aur bhi sanadon sey bayan hui hai. 3- ehle-ilm (aalimon) ka is par amal hai ke wuzu key ang ko eik eik baar dhona kafi hai, do-do baar afzal hai aur is se bhi ziyada afzal teen-teen baar dhona hai. is sey aagey ki gunjaaish nahin. ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain : jab koi wuzu key ang ko teen baar sey ziyada dhoey to mujhey uskey gunah mein padney ka khatra hai. Imam Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : teen sey zayed baar wuzu key ang ko wohi dhoeyga jo (deewangi aur waswase) mein mubtala hoga."
45,"mainey Abu Jaafar sey puchha : kya Jabir Raziallahu Anhuma ney aap sey ye bayan kiya hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu key ang eik eik baar , do do baar , aur teen teen baar dhoey hain? to unhon-ney kaha : ji haan (bayan kiya hai)."
46,"aap sey Jabir Raziallahu anhuma ney ye bayan kiya hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu key ang ko eik baar dho diya, unhoney jawab diya : ji haan. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- aur ye Shareek ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai kyonkey ye Sabit sey Wakee ki riwayat ki tarah aur bhi kaee sanadon sey bayan hui hai. 2- aur Shareek ziyaada ghalat Raavi hain."
47,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu kiya to aap ney apna chehra teen baar dhoya aur apney dono haath do-do baar dhoey phir apney sar ka masah kiya aur apney dono pair do-do baar dhoey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai 2- iskey ilawa aur bhi hadeeson mein ye baat mazkur hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney baaz wuzu key ang ko eik eik baar aur baaz ko teen teen baar dhoyaa. 3- baaz ehle-ilm (aalimon) ney is baat ki ijazat di hai. un ki raey mein wuzu mein baaz aa'zaa (angon) ko teen baar, baaz ko do baar aur baaz ko eik baar dhoney mein koi harj nahin."
48,"mainey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney wuzu kiya to apney dono pahunchey dhoey yahan tak ke unhen khub saaf kiya, phir teen baar kulli ki, teen baar naak mein pani chadhaya , teen baar apna chehra dhoya phir teen daf'a baazu dhoey aur eik baar apney sar ka masah kiya, phir apney dono paaon takhnon tak dhoey, phir khadey huye aur wuzu sey bachey huye pani ko khadey khadey pi liya. phir kaha : mainey tumhen dikhaana chaha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka wuzu kaisey hota tha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Usman , Abdullah bin Zaid , ibne-Abbas , Abdullah bin Amr , Rabee , Abdullah bin Anees aur Aaisha (rizwanullahi-alaihim) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
49,jab wo apney wuzu sey farigh huye to bachey huye pani ko unhoney apney chullu mein liya aur usey piya. Imam Tirmizi ney is hadees key mukhtalif tark zikr karney key baad farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
50,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''merey paas Jibreel ney aa kar kaha : aey Muhammad ! jab aap wuzu karen to  sharmgaah par) pani chhidak lein.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko ye kehtey suna hai ke Hasan bin Ali Hashmi munkirul-hadees Raavi hain. 3- is hadees ki sanad mein log iztirab (bechaini) ka shikar hain. 4- is bab mein Abul-Hakam bin Sufiyaan, ibne-Abbas , Zaid bin Harisa aur Abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
51,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisi cheezen na bataaun jin sey Allah gunahon ko mitata aur darjaat ko buland karta hai?'' logon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kyon nahin, aap zarur bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''nagawari key bawajud mukammal wuzu karna padhi. aur masjidon ki taraf ziyada chal kar jana padhi. aur namaz key baad namaz ka intizar karna , yehi sarhad ki haqeeqi pasbani hai.''"
52,"lekin Quteba ney apni riwayat mein « فذلكم الرباط فذلكم الرباط فذلكم الرباط » teen baar kaha hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is baab mein Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Abdullah bin Amr , ibne-Abbas , Ubeda ya Ubeda bin Amr' Aaisha , Abdur-Rehman bin Aaish Hizrami aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
53,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key paas eik kapda tha jis sey aap wuzu key baad apna badan ponchhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki riwayat durust nahin hai Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey is baab mein koi bhi riwayat sahih nahin hai, abu-Muaz Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Arqam muhaddeseen key nazdik zaeef hain. 2- is bab mein Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
54,"mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap wuzu kartey to chehrey ko apney kapdey key kinarey sey ponchhtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai aur iski sanad zaeef hai, Rushdain bin Saad aur Abdur-Rehman bin Ziyad bin Anam Afriqi dono hadees mein zaeef qarar diye jatey hain. 2- Sahaba kiram aur unkey baad key logon mein sey ehle-ilm (aalimon) key eik giroh ney wuzu key baad roomaal sey pochhney ki ijazat di hai, aur jin logon ney isey makrooh kaha hai to mehaz is wajeh sey kaha hai ke kaha jata hai : wuzu ko (qiyamat key din) tola jaeyga, ye baat Saeed bin Musaiyab aur Zohri sey riwayat ki gaee hai. 3- Zohri kehtey hain ke wuzu key baad tauliya ka istimal isliye makrooh hai ke wuzu ka pani (qiyamat key roz) tola jaeyga."
55,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''jo wuzu karey aur achchhi tarah karey phir yun kahe : (أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له وأشهد أن محمدا عبده ورسوله اللهم اجعلني من التوابين واجعلني من المتطهرين) ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin wo akela hai, uska koi shareek nahin, aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad uskey bandey aur Rasool hain, aey Allah ! mujhey tauba karney walon aur pak rehney walon mein sey bana dey'' to uskey liye jannat key aathon darwazey khol diye jaeyngey wo jis sey bhi chahey jannat mein dakhil ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Anas aur Aqba bin Aamir Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- Imam Tirmizi ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees key turq padhi. zikr karney key baad farmaya ke is hadees ki sanad mein iztirab (ikhtilaaf) hai. 3- 2- is bab mein ziyadatar cheezen Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey sahih sabit nahin hain."
56,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eik mudd pani sey wuzu aur eik saa pani sey ghusl farmatey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1-safeena ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Jabir aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ki raey yehi hai ke eik mudd pani sey wuzu kiya jaey aur eik saa pani sey ghusl. Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke is hadees ka maqsad mehdood karna nahin hai ke is sey ziyada ya kam jayez nahin balke matlab ye hai ke ye miqdaar aisi hai jo kafi hoti hai."
57,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''wuzu key liye eik shetan hai. usey Walhaan kaha jata hai,. tum uskey waswason key sabab pani ziyada kharch karney sey bacho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abdullah bin Amr aur Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- Ubai bin Kaab ki hadees gharib hai. 3- iski sanad muhaddeseen key nazdik qawi nahin hai isliye ke hum nahin jantey ke Khaarija key ilawa kisi aur ney isey sanad ke saath riwayat kiya ho, ye hadees dusri aur sanadon sey Hasan (Basri) sey mauqufan riwayat hui hai. (yani isey Hasan hi ka qol qarar diya gaya hai) aur is baab mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey koi chiz sahih nahin aur Khaarija hamarey as-haab (saatiyon)  key nazdik ziyada qawi nahin hain. ibne-Mubarak ney unki tazeef ki hai (zaeef kaha hai)."
58,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har namaz key liye wuzu kartey baa-wuzoo hotey ya be-wuzu. Humed kehtey hain ke mainey Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : aap log kaisey kartey they? to unhon-ney kaha ke hum eik hi wuzu kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Humed ki hadees ba-wasta Anas is sanad sey gharib hai, aur muhaddeseen key nazdik mashhoor Amr bin Aamir wali hadees hai jo ba-wasta Anas bayan hui hai. aur baaz ehle-ilm padhi. ki raey hai ke har namaz key liye wuzu mustahab hai na ke wajib."
59,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''jo wuzu par wuzu kareyga Allah uskey liye das nekiyan likheyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Afriqi ney Abu Ghutaif sey aur Abu Ghutaif ney ibne-Umar sey aur ibne-Umar ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey riwayat ki hai. hum sey isey Husain bin Hures Marwazi ney Muhammad bin Yazeed Waasti key wastey sey bayan kiya hai aur Muhammad bin Yazeed ney Afriqi sey riwayat ki hai aur ye sanad zaeef hai. 2- Ali bin Madeeni kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed Al Qattaan kehtey hain : unhon-ney is hadees ka zikr Hisham bin Urwa sey kiya to unhon-ney kaha ke ye sanad mashriqi hai. 3- mainey Ahmed bin Hasan ko kehtey huye suna ke mainey Ahmed bin Hanbal ko kehtey suna hai : mainey apni aankh sey Yahya bin Saeed Al Qattan ki tarah kisi ko nahin dekha.
60,"mainey Anas bin Maalik ko ye kehtey huye suna : Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har namaz key liye wuzu kartey they, mainey (Anas sey) puchha : phir aap log kaisey kartey they? to unhon-ney kaha ke jab tak hum (naapaaki) na kartey sari namazein eik hi wuzu sey padhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur Humed ki hadees jo Anas sey riwayet hui hai. gharib Hasan hai."
61,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har namaz key liye wuzu kartey they, aur jab Fateh Makka ka saal huwa to aap ney kaee namazein eik wuzu sey ada kin aur apney mozon par masah kya, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya ke aap ney eik aisi chiz ki hai jisey kabhi nahin kya tha? aap ney farmaya : ''main ney isey jan-bujh kar kya hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur is hadees ko Ali bin Qadim ney bhi Sufiyan Sory sey riwayat kya hai aur unhoney is mein itna izafa kya hai ke '' aap ney wuzu key ang ko eik eik baar dhoya '' 3- Sufiyan Sory ney basanad « Maharib bin dassaar an Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Barida » ( mursalan riwayat kya hai) ke '' Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) har namaz key liye wuzu kartey they '' 4- aur usey Wakee ney basanad « Sufiyan an Maharib an Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Barida an Barida » sey riwayat kya hai, 5- neez usey Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi waghera ney basanad « Sufiyan an Maharib bin dassaar an Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Barida » mursalan riwayat kya hai, aur ye riwayat Wakee ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai padhi. , 6- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke eik wuzu sey kaee namazein ada ki ja sakti hain, jab tak « hadas » na ho, 7- baaz ehle-ilm Istehbab aur fazilat key iradey sey har namaz key liye wuzu kartey they, 8- neez Abdur-Rehman Afriqi ney basanad « abi Ghatfain ibne-Umar » riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jo wuzu par wuzu kerega to uski wajeh sey Allah uskey liye das nekiyan likhega'' is hadees ki sanad zaeef hai, 9- 2- is bab mein Jabir bin Abdullah sey bhi riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney eik wuzu sey Zohar aur Asr dono padhin."
62,"mujh sey Memuna (Raziallahu Anha) ney bayan kya ke main aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dono eik hi bartan sey ghusle-janabat kartey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aksar fuqaha ka yehi qol hai ke mard aur aurat key eik hi bartan sey ghusl karney mein koi harj nahin, 3- 2- is bab mein Ali , Aaisha , Anas , Umme-Haani , Umme-Habiba , Umme-Salma aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
63,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney aurat key wuzu sey bachey huye pani sey) wuzu karney sey) mana farmaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abdullah bin sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- baaz fuqaha ney aurat key wuzu sey bachey huye pani sey wuzu karney ko makrooh qarar diya hai, yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, un dono ney aurat key wuzu sey bachey huye pani ko makrooh kaha hai lekin uskey jhootey key istimal mein un dono ney koi harj nahin jana."
64,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney aurat key wuzu sey bachey huye pani sey wuzu ko mana farmaya hai, ya farmaya : aurat key jhootey sey wuzu kerey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- aur Muhammad bin Bashaar apni hadees mein kehtey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya ke mard aurat key wuzu sey bachey huye pani sey wuzu kerey. aur Muhammad bin Bashaar ney us riwayat mein - « أو بسؤرها » wala shak bayan nahin kya."
65,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki eik biwi ney eik lagan (tab) sey) pani ley kar) ghusl kya, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney us ( bachey huye pani ( sey wuzu karna chaha, to unhoney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! main napak thi, aap ney farmaya : pani junbi nahin hota padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- yehi Sufiyan Sory, Malik aur Shafai ka qol hai."
66,"arz kya gaya : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum Bizaa naami kunwen padhi. sey wuzu karen aur haal ye hai wo eik aisa kunwaan hai jis mein haiz key kapdey , kutton key gosht aur badbudar cheezen aa kar girti hain? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' pani pak hai usey koi chiz napak nahin karti '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- biar Bizaa wali abu Saeed Khudri ki ye hadees jis umdagi key sath abu-Usaama ney riwayat ki hai kisi aur ney riwayat nahin ki hai, 3- ye hadees kaee aur tareeq sey abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai, 4- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
67,"mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey suna , aap sey us pani key barey mein puchha ja raha tha jo maidan mein hota hai aur jis par darindey aur chopaey aatey jatey hain, to aap ney farmaya : '' jab pani do qulla padhi. ho to wo gandagi ko asar andaz honey nahin dega, usey dafa kar dega''. Muhammad bin Is-haq kehtey hain : qulla sey murad ghadey hain aur qulla wo ( dol ( bhi hai jis sey kheton aur baghaat ki seenchai ki jati hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- yehi qol Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka hai. un logon ka kehna hai ke jab pani do qulla ho to usey koi chiz najas nahin kar sakti jab tak ke uski bu ya maza badal na jaey, aur un logon ka kehna hai ke do qulla paanch mushk key qarib hota hai."
68,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey koi aadmi thehrey huye pani padhi. mein peshab na karey phir us sey wuzu karey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
69,"eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! hum samandar ka safar kartey hain aur apney sath thoda pani ley jatey hain, agar hum us sey wuzu kar lein to piyasey reh jaeyngey, to kya aisi surat mein hum samandar key pani sey wuzu kar saktey hain? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' samandar ka pani pak padhi. hai, aur uska murdar halal hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir bin Abdullah aur Farasi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- aur yehi Sahaba kiram (Raziallauh anhum) mein sey aksar fuqaha ka qol hai jin mein abu-Bakar , umr aur ibne-Abbas bhi hain ke samandar key pani sey wuzu karney mein koi harj nahin, baaz Sahaba kiram ney samandar key pani sey wuzu ko makrooh jana hai, unhi mein ibne-Umar aur Abdullah bin Amr hain Abdullah bin Amr ka kehna hai ke samandar ka pani aag hai."
70,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar do qabron key paas sey huwa to aap ney farmaya : '' ye dono qabr waley azab diye ja rahey hain, aur kisi badi chiz mein azab nahin diye ja rahey (ke jis sey bachna mushkil hota ( raha ye to ye apney peshab sey bachta nahin tha padhi. aur raha ye to ye chughlii kya karta tha '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , abu-Musa , Abdur-Rehman bin Hasna , Zaid bin Sabit , aur abu-Bakra (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
71,"mein apney bachey ko ley kar Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key paas aai , wo abhi tak khana nahin khata tha padhi. , usney aap par peshab kar diya to aap ney pani mangwaya aur usey is par chhidak liya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali , Aaisha , Zenab , Fazal bin Abbas ki walida lubaaba bint Haris , abu-Samah , Abdullah bin Amr , abu-Leila aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram , Tabe-een aur unkey baad key logon ka yehi qol hai ke bachey key peshab par pani chhidka jaey aur bachi ka peshab dhoya jaey, aur ye hukm us waqt tak hai jab tak ke wo dono khana na khaney lag jaeyn, aur jab wo khana khaney lag jaeyn to bil-ittefaq dono ka peshab dhoya jaeyga."
72,"qabila uraina key kuch log Madina aaye , unhen Madina ki aab o huwa raas na aai , chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney unhen zakat key oonton mein bhej diya aur farmaya : '' tum unkey doodh aur peshab piyo '' ( wo wahan gaey aur kha pi kar motey ho gaey ( to un logon ney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key charwahey ko maar dala , oonton ko haank ley gaey, aur Islam sey murtad ho gaey, unhen ( pakad kar) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key paas laya gaya, aap ney unkey eik taraf key haath aur dusri taraf key paon katwaa diye , un ki aakhon mein salaaiyan pher den aur garm tapti hui zamin mein unhen phenk diya . Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : mainey un mein sey eik shakhs ko dekha tha ke) wo piyas bujhaney key liye (apney munh sey zamin chaat raha tha yahan tak ke wo usi haalat mein mar gaey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, aur kaee sanadon sey Anas sey marvi hai, 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai ke jis janwer ka gosht khaya jata ho uskey peshab mein koi harj nahin."
73,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney un ki aakhon mein salaaiyan isliye pherein ke un logon ney bhi charwaahon ki aakhon mein salaaiyan pheri thin . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- aur Allah Taala key farman «wl-juruhul qisaas » ka yehi mafhoom hai, Muhammad bin Sirin sey marvi hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney unkey sath ye maamla hudood ( sazaon ( key nazil honey sey pehley kya tha."
74,Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' wuzu wajib nahin jab tak aawaz na ho ya bo na aaye ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
75,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi masjid mein ho aur wo apni peeth sey hawa nikalney ka shubha paey to wo ( masjid sey) na nikley jab tak ke wo hawa key khaarij honey ki aawaz na sun ley , ya baghair aawaz key pet sey khaarij honey wali hawa ki bo na mehsus kar ley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Zaid, Ali bin Talaq , Aaisha , ibne-Abbas , ibne-Masood aur abu Saeed Khudri sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. - aur yehi ulama ka qol hai ke wuzu « hadas » hi sey wajib hota hai ke wo « hadas » ki aawaz sun ley ya bo mehsus kar ley , Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain ke jab « hadas » mein shak ho to wuzu wajib nahin hota , jab tak ke aisa yaqin na ho jaey ke is par qism kha sakey , neez kehtey hain ke jab aurat ki agli sharmgaah sey hawa khaarij ho to is par wuzu wajib ho jata hai, yehi Shafai aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
76,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein kisi ko « hadas » ho jaey ( yani uska wuzu toot jaey ( padhi. to Allah uski namaz qubul nahin karta jab tak ke wo wuzu na kar ley ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
77,"mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap sajdey ki haalat mein so gaey, yahan tak ke aap kharrantey leney lagey, phir khadey ho kar namaz padhney lagey, to mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool! aap to so gaey they? aap ney farmaya : '' wuzu sirf is par wajib hota hai jo chit let kar soey isliye ke jab aadmi let jata hai to uskey jod dhiley ho jatey hain'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Aaisha , ibne-Masood , aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
78,"Sahaba kiram (Raziallauh anhum) ( bethey bethey ( so jatey , phir uth kar namaz padhtey aur wuzu nahin kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- mainey Saleh bin Abdullah ko ye kehtey huye suna ke mainey Abdullah ibne-Mubarak sey us aadmi key barey mein puchha jo bethey bethey so jaey to unhoney kaha ke is par wuzu nahin, 3- ibne-Abbas wali hadees ko Saeed bin abi Aruba ney basanad « Qatada an ibne-Abbas » ( moqufan ( riwayat kya hai aur is mein abul-Aaliya ka zikr nahin kya hai, 4- neend sey wuzu key silsiley mein ulama ka ikhtilaf hai, aksar ehle-ilm ki raey yehi hai ke koi khadey khadey so jaey to is par wuzu nahin jab tak ke wo let kar na soey , yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak aur Ahmed kehtey hain, aur baaz logon ney kaha hai ke jab neend is qadr gehri ho ke aql par ghalib aa jaey to is par wuzu wajib hai aur yehi Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain, Shafai ka kehna hai ke jo shakhs bethey bethey soey aur khuwab dekhney lag jaey, ya neend key ghalba sey uski peeth apni jagah sey hat jaey to is par wuzu wajib hai padhi. ."
79,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya '' aag par paki hui chiz sey wuzu hai agar-che wo paneer ka koi tukda hi kyon na ho '' , is par ibne-Abbas ney un sey kaha : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu)) bataiye ( kya hum ghii aur garm pani ( key istimal ( sey bhi wuzu keren? to Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : bhatijey ! tum jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki koi hadees suno to us par) amal karo) baaten na banao .) aur misalen bayan kar key qiyas na karo) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Umme-Habiba , Umme-Salma , Zaid bin Sabit , abu-Talha , abu-Ayyub Ansari aur abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ki raey hai ke aag sey paki hui chiz sey wuzu hai, lekin Sahaba , Tabe-een aur unkey baad key logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka mazhab hai ke us sey wuzu nahin, ( daleel agli hadees hai) ."
80,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( Madina mein) nikley , main aap key sath tha, aap eik Ansari aurat key paas aaye , usney aap key liye eik bakri zibeh ki aap ney (usey) khaya , wo tar khajuron ka eik tabaq bhi ley kar aai to aap ney is mein sey bhi khaya , phir Zohar key liye wuzu kya aur Zohar ki namaz padhi , aap ney wapis palatney ka irada kya hi tha ke wo bakri key bachey huye gosht mein sey kuch gosht ley kar aai to aap ney ( usey bhi) khaya , phir aap ney Asr ki namaz padhi aur) dobara ( wuzu nahin kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq , ibne-Abbas , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Masood , abu-Raafey , Ummul-Hakam, Amr bin Umayya , Ummey-Aamir, Suwed bin No'man aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. abu-Bakar ki wo hadees jisey ibne-Abbas ney un sey riwayat kya hai sanadan zaeef hai ibne-Abbas ki marfooan hadees ziyada sahih hai aur huffaz ney aisey hi riwayat kya hai. 2- Sahaba kiram Tabe-een aur unkey baad key logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm maslan Sufiyan Sory ibne-Mubarak Shafai Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka isi par amal hai ke aag par paki hui chiz sey wuzu wajib nahin, aur yehi Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aakhiri kaam hai, goya ye hadees pehli hadees ki naasikh hai jis mein hai ke aag ki paki hui chiz sey wuzu toot jata hai۔"
81,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey oont key gosht key barey puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : is sey wuzu karo aur bakri key gosht key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : '' us sey wuzu na karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Jabir bin Samra aur Usaid bin Huzer Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- yehi qol Ahmed , Abdullah aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka hai, 3- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke is baab mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey do hadisein sahih hain : eik Bara bin Aazib ki) jisey muallif ney zikr kya aur uskey turq par behes ki hai) aur dusri Jabir bin Samra ki, 4- yehi qol Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka hai. aur Tabe-een waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm sey marvi hai ke un logon ki raey hai ke oont key gosht sey wuzu nahin hai aur yehi Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka qol hai padhi. ."
82,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jo apni sharmgaah ( uzue-tanasul ( chhuey to jab tak wuzu na kar ley namaz na padhey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Busra ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Umme-Habiba , abu-Ayyub , Abu-Hurera , Arwa bint Unais , Aaisha , Jabir , Zaid bin Khalid aur Abdullah bin umr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- kaee logon ney isey isi tarah Hisham bin Urwa sey aur Hisham ney apney walid ( Urwa ( sey aur Urwa ney Busra sey riwayat kya hai padhi. ."
83,is hadees ko basanad « Hisham bin Urwa an Abiy an Marwan Busra an Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) » riwayat kya hai.
84,"« basanad Urwa an Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) » isi tarah riwayat kya hai. 1- yehi Sahaba aur Tabe-een mein sey kaee logon ka qol hai aur usi key qaail Auzaai , Shafai , Ahmed , aur Is-haq bin Raahviya hain, 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke Busra ki hadees is baab mein sab sey sahih hai, 2- abu-Zaraa kehtey hain ke Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees padhi. ( bhi) is baab mein sahih hai, 4- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke makhool ka samaa, Anbasa bin abi Sufiyan sey nahin hai, aur Makhool ney eik aadmi sey aur us aadmi ney Anbasa sey un ki hadees key ilawa eik dusri hadees riwayat ki hai, goya Imam Bukhari is hadees ko sahih nahin mantey ."
85,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney ( uzue-tanasul key silsiley mein) farmaya : '' ye to jism hi ka eik loathra ya tukda hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram mein sey kaee logon sey neez baaz Tabe-een sey bhi marvi hai ke uzue-tanasul key chhuney sey wuzu wajib nahin, aur yehi ehle-koofa aur ibne-Mubarak ka qol hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein marvi ahadees mein sey ye sab sey achi hadees hai, 4- Ayub bin Utba aur Muhammad bin Jabir ney bhi is hadees ko Qais bin Talaq ney « an Abiy » sey riwayat kya hai. baaz muhaddeseen ney Muhammad bin Jabir aur Ayub bin Utba key silsiley mein kalam kya hai, 5- mulaazim bin Amr ki hadees jisey unhoney Abdullah bin Badr sey riwayat kya hai, sab sey sahih aur achi hai padhi. ."
86,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney apni biwiyon mein sey kisi eik ka bosa liya , phir aap namaz key liye nikley aur wuzu nahin kya, Urwa kehtey hain ke mainey ( apni khaala ummul-momenin Aaisha sey) kaha : wo aap hi rahi hongi ? to wo hans padin . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey kaee ehle-ilm sey isi tarah marvi hai aur yehi qol Sufiyan Sory , aur ehle-koofa ka hai ke bosa leney sey wuzu ( wajib ( nahin hai, Malik bin Anas , Auzaai , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke bosa leney sey wuzu ( wajib ( hai, yehi qol Sahaba aur Tabe-een mein sey bahut sey ehle-ilm ka hai, 2- hamarey as-haab ney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees par jo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey riwayat ki hai mehaz is wajeh sey amal nahin kya ke ye sanad key aetbar sey sahih nahin, 3- Yahya bin Qataan ney is hadees ki bahut ziyada tazeef ki hai aur kaha hai ke ye «la shey» key mushabeh hai padhi. , 4- neez mainey Muhammad bin Ismail ( Bukhari ( ko bhi is hadees ki tazeef kartey suna , unhoney kaha ke Habib bin Sabit ka samaa, Urwa sey nahin hai, 5- neez Ibrahim Taimi ney bhi Aaisha sey riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney unka bosa liya aur wuzu nahin kya۔ lekin ye riwayat bhi sahih nahin kyonkey Aaisha sey Ibrahim Temi key samaa, ka hamen ilm nahin۔ is baab mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey koi bhi hadees sahih nahin hai."
87,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney qai ki to roza tod diya aur wuzu kya ( Maadaan kehtey hain ke) phir mainey Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey dimashq ki masjid mein mulaqat ki aur mainey un sey is baat ka zikr kya to unhoney kaha ke Abu-Darda ney sach kaha , mainey hi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par pani dala tha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sahaba aur Tabe-een mein sey bahut sey ehle-ilm ki raey hai ke qai aur Nakseer sey wuzu ( toot jata ( hai. aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Ahmed , aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai padhi. aur baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha hai ke qai aur Nakseer sey wuzu nahin toot-ta ye Malik aur Shafai ka qol hai, 2- hadees key turq ko zikr karney key baad Imam Tirmizi farmatey hain ke Husen al-Muallim ki hadees is baab mein sab sey sahih hai."
88,"mujh sey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney puchha : '' tumharey mishkeezey mein kya hai? '' to mainey arz kya : nabeez hai padhi. , aap ney farmaya : '' khajoor bhi pak hai aur pani bhi pak hai'' to aap ney usi sey wuzu kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Zaid muhaddeseen key nazdik majhool aadmi hain is hadees key ilawa koi aur riwayat un sey jaani nahin jati, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ki raey hai nabeez sey wuzu jayez hai unhi mein sey Sufiyan Sory waghera hain, baaz ehle-ilm ney kaha hai ke nabeez sey wuzu jayez nahin padhi. ye Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai, Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke agar kisi aadmi ko yehi karna pad jaey to wo nabeez sey wuzu kar key tayammum kar ley , ye merey nazdik ziyada pasandida hai, 3- jo log nabeez sey wuzu ko jayez nahin mantey unka qol Quran sey ziyada qarib aur ziyada qarin qiyas hai isliye ke Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : « فإن لم تجدوا ماء فتيمموا صعيدا طيبا » '' jab tum pani na paao Tu Pak mitti sey tayammum kar lo '' ( Nisa : 43 ( puri aayat yun hai : یٰۤاَیُّہَا الَّذِیۡنَ اٰمَنُوۡا لَا تَقۡرَبُوا الصَّلٰوۃَ وَ اَنۡتُمۡ سُکٰرٰی حَتّٰی تَعۡلَمُوۡا مَا تَقُوۡلُوۡنَ وَ لَا جُنُبًا اِلَّا عَابِرِیۡ سَبِیۡلٍ حَتّٰی تَغۡتَسِلُوۡا padhi. وَ اِنۡ کُنۡتُمۡ مَّرۡضٰۤی اَوۡ عَلٰی سَفَرٍ اَوۡ جَآءَ اَحَدٌ مِّنۡکُمۡ مِّنَ الۡغَآئِطِ اَوۡ لٰمَسۡتُمُ النِّسَآءَ فَلَمۡ تَجِدُوۡا مَآءً فَتَیَمَّمُوۡا صَعِیۡدًا طَیِّبًا فَامۡسَحُوۡا بِوُجُوۡہِکُمۡ وَ اَیۡدِیۡکُمۡ padhi. اِنَّ اللّٰہَ  کَانَ عَفُوًّا غَفُوۡرًا ﴿۴۳﴾"
89,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney doodh piya to pani mangwaya kar kulli ki aur farmaya : '' is mein chiknai hoti hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Sehal bin Saad Saaidi , aur Umme-Salma Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ki raey hai ke kulli doodh peeney sey hai, aur ye hukm hamarey nazdik mustahab padhi. hai."
90,"eik shakhs ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya, aap peshab kar rahey they, to aap ney uskey salam ka jawab nahin diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur hamarey nazdik salam ka jawab dena us surat mein makrooh qarar diya jata hai jab aadmi pakhana ya peshab kar raha ho, baaz ehle-ilm ney uski yehi tafseer ki hai, 3- ye sab sey umda hadees hai jo is baab mein riwayat ki gaee hai, 4- aur is baab mein Muhajir bin Qanfaz, Abdullah bin Hanzala, Alqama bin Shafwa, Jabir aur Bara bin Aazib (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
91,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' bartan mein jab kutta munh dal dey to usey saat baar dhoya jaey, pehli baar ya aakhiri baar usey mitti sey dhoya jaey padhi. , aur jab billi munh daley to usey eik baar dhoya jaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. 3- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey kaee sanadon sey isi tarah marvi hai jin mein billi key munh dalney par eik baar dhoney ka zikr nahin kya gaya hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
92,"abu-Qatada merey paas aaye to mainey unkey liye (eik bartan ( wuzu ka pani mein dala , itney main eik billi aa kar peeney lagi to unhoney bartan ko uskey liye jhuka diya taake wo ( aasani sey) pi ley , Kabsha kehti hain : abu-Qatada ney mujhey dekha ke main un ki taraf tajjub sey dekh rahi hun to unhoney kaha : bhatiji ! kya tum ko tajjub ho raha hai? mainey kaha : ji haan , to unhoney kaha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya hai : '' ye ( billi ( najas nahin, ye to tumharey paas barabar aaney janey walon ya aaney janey waaliyon mein sey hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Aaisha aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees marvi hain, 2- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 3- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een aur unkey baad key logon mein sey aksar ehle-ilm maslan Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai ke billi key jhootey mein koi harj nahin, aur ye sab sey achi hadees hai jo is baab mein riwayat ki gaee hai."
93,"Jareer bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma ney peshab kya phir wuzu kya aur apney mozon par masah kya, un sey kaha gaya : kya aap aisa kar rahey hain? to unhoney kaha ke mujhey us kaam sey kon si chiz rok sakti hai jabkey mainey khud Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aisa kartey dekha hai, Ibrahim Nakhai kehtey hain ke Sahaba kiram ko Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees achi lagti thi kyonkey unka Islam Sura al-Maeyda key nuzool key baad ka hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Ali , Huzefa , Mughira , Bilal , abu-Ayyub , Salman , Barida , Amr bin Umayya , Anas , Sehal bin Saad , Yala bin Murra , Ubada bin Samit , Usama bin shareek , abu-Umama , Jabir , Usama bin Zaid , ibne-Ibada jinhen ibn Imaara aur Ubai-bin Imaara bhi kaha jata hai (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
94,"mainey Jareer bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma ko dekha ke unhoney wuzu kya aur apney mozon par masah kya, mainey jab un sey is silsiley mein baat ki to unhoney kaha : mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney wuzu kya aur apney mozon par masah kya, mainey un sey puchha : aap ka ye amal Sura al-Maeyda key nuzool sey pehley ka hai, ya baad ka ? to kaha : main to Sura al-Maeyda utarney key baad hi Islam laya hun, ye hadees aayat wuzu ki tafseer kar rahi hai isliye ke jin logon ney mozon par masah ka inkar kya hai un mein sey baaz ney ye taaweel ki hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney mozon par jo masah kya tha wo aayat Maeyda key nuzool sey pehley ka tha, jabkey Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) ney apni riwayat mein zikr kya hai ke unhoney nuzool Maeyda key baad Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mozon par masah kartey huye dekha hai."
95,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey mozon par masah key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : '' musafir key liye teen din hai aur muqeem key liye eik din ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Yahya bin moayan sey manqul hai ke unhoney masah key silsiley mein Khuzema bin Sabit ki hadees ko sahih qarar diya hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali, abu-Bakra, abu-Huraira, Safwan bin Assal, Auf bin Malik, ibne-Umar aur Jareer (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
96,"jab hum musafir hotey to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamen hukm detey ke hum apney mozey teen din aur teen raat tak , peshab , pakhana ya neend ki wajeh sey na utaaren , illa ye ke janabat laahiq ho jaey padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Muhammad bin Ismail ( Bukhari ( kehtey hain ke is baab mein Safwan bin Assaal muradi ki hadees sab sey umda hai, 3- aksar Sahaba kiram , Tabe-een aur unkey baad key fuqaha mein sey aksar ehle-ilm maslan : Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai ke muqeem eik din aur eik raat mozon par masah karey , aur musafir teen din aur teen raat , baaz ulama sey marvi hai ke mozon par masah key liye waqt ki tehdeed nahin ki (jab tak dil chahey kar sakta hai) ye Malik bin Anas (Rahimahullah) ka qol hai, lekin tahdeed wala qol ziyada sahih hai."
97,"akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney mozey key ooper aur nichey dono janib masah kya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sahaba kiraam, Tabe-een aur unkey baad key fuqaha mein sey bahut sey logon ka yehi qol hai aur Malik , Shafai aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain, 2- ye hadees maalul hai. mainey abu-Zara'a aur Muhammad bin Ismail ( Bukhari ( sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to un dono ney kaha ke ye sahih nahin hai padhi. ."
98,"mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mozon key oopri hissey par masah kartey dekha padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- Abdur-Rehman bin abi Zinad key ilawa mein kisi aur ko nahin janta jisney basanad « Urwa an Mughira » dono mozon key '' oopri hissey '' par masah ka zikr karta ho padhi. aur yehi kaee ehle-ilm ka qol hai aur yehi Sufiyan Sory aur Ahmed bhi kehtey hain."
99,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu kya aur mozon aur jooton par masah kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- kaee ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai aur Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain ke patabon par masah karey halanki jootay na hon jabke paata be motey hun, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat aai hai, 4- abu-Muqatil samarqandi kehtey hain ke main abu-Hanifa key paas un ki us bimari mein gaya jis mein un ki wafat hui to unhoney pani mangaaya, aur wuzu kya, wo paatabe pehney huye they, to unhoney un par masah kya, phir kaha : aaj mainey aisa kaam kya hai jo main nahin karta tha۔ mainey patabon par masah kya hai halanke mainey jootiyaan nahin pehan rakhin۔"
100,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney wuzu kya aur dono mozon aur amaamey par masah kya. Muhammad bin Bashaar ney eik dusri jagah is hadees mein ye zikr kya hai ke '' aap ney apni peshani aur apney amaamey par masah kya '' , ye hadees aur bhi kaee sanadon sey Mughira bin Shoba sey riwayat ki gaee hai, un mein sey baaz ney peshani aur amaamey par masah ka zikr kya hai aur baaz ney peshani ka zikr nahin kya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Amr bin Umayya , Salman , Soban aur abu-Umama (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- Sahaba kiram mein sey kaee ehle-ilm ka bhi yehi qol hai. un mein sey abu-Bakar , umr aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) hain aur Auzaai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain ke amaama par masah karey , Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey bahut sey ehle-ilm ka kehna hai ke amaamey par masah nahin siwaye us surat key ke amaama key sath ( kuch ( sar ka bhi masah kerey۔ Sufiyan Sory , Malik bin Anas , ibne-Mubarak aur Shafai usi key qaail hain, 4- Wakee bin Jarrah kehtey hain ke agar koi amaamey par masah kar ley to hadees ki ro sey ye usey kafi hoga."
101,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney dono mozon par aur amaamey par masah kiya.
102,mainey Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey dono mozon par masah key barey mein puchha to unhon-ney kaha : merey bhatijey ! (ye) sunnat hai. wo kehtey hain aur mainey amama par masah key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : baalon ko chhuoo.
103,"mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key liye nahaney ka pani rakha , aap ney ghusle-janabat (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat) kiya, to bartan ko apney baaein hath sey daain haath par jhukaya aur apney pahunchey dhoey, phir apna haath bartan mein dala aur sharmgaah par pani bahaayaa, phir apna haath deewar ya zamin par ragdaa. phir kulli ki aur naak mein pani dala aur apna chehra dhoya aur apney dono haath dhoey. phir teen martaba sar par pani bahaayaa, phir purey jism par pani bahaayaa , phir wahan sey parey hat kar apney paaon dhoey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Umme-Salma, Jabir , abu-Saeed Juber bin Mut-im aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
104,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat) ka irada kartey to haathon ko bartan mein dakhil karney sey pehley dhotey , phir sharmgaah dhotey , aur apni namaz key wuzu ki tarah wuzu kartey , phir baal pani sey bhigotey , phir apney sar par teen lap pani daltey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi ko ehle-ilm (aalimon) ney ghusle-janabat (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat) mein ikhtiyar kiya hai ke wo namaz key wuzu ki tarah wuzu karey , phir apney sar par teen baar pani daley , phir apney purey badan par pani bahaaey , phir apney paon dhoey , ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, isi ke saath in logon ney kaha ke agar junbi (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insan) pani mein gotaa maarey aur wuzu na karey to ye usey kafi ho ga. yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
105,"mainey arz kiya, Allah key Rasool ! main apney sar ki choti mazbooti sey baandhney wali aurat hun. kya ghusle-janabat (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat) key liye isey khola karun? aap ney farmaya : ''tumhari sar par teen lap pani dal lena hi kafi hai. phir purey badan par pani baha do Tu Pak ho qaee, ya farmaya : jab tum aisa kar lo Tu Pak ho gaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, ehle-ilm (aalimon) ka isi par amal  hai ke aurat jab janabat (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat) ka ghusl karey , aur apney baal na kholey to ye uskey liye uskey baad ke wo apney sar par pani baha ley kafi ho jaeyga."
106,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''har baal key nichey janabat ka asar hota hai, isliye baalon ko achchhi tarah dhoya karo aur khaal ko achchhi tarah malkar saaf karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali aur Anas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- Haris bin Wajeeh ki hadees gharib hai, isey hum sirf unhin ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur wo qawi nahin hain, wo is hadees ko Malik bin Dinar sey riwayat karney mein munfarid (alag) hain."
107,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusl key baad wuzu nahin kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey kaee ehle-ilm (aalimon) ka qol hai ke ghusl key baad wuzu na karey.
108,"jab mard key khatna ka maqam (uzue-tanasul) aurat key khatney key maqam (sharmgaah) sey mil jaey to ghusl wajib ho gaya padhi. , mainey aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney aisa kiya to hamney ghusl kiya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin Amr aur Raafey bin khadij (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
109,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''jab mard key khatney ka maqam aurat key khatney key maqam (sharmgaah) sey mil jaey to ghusl wajib ho gaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- kaee sanadon sey Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) marfoo hadees riwayet hui hai ke ''jab khatney ka maqam khatney key maqam sey mil jaey to ghusl wajib ho jata hai'' Sahaba kiram mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai. unmein Abu-Bakar , umr , Usman , Ali aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) bhi shamil hain. Tabe-een aur unkey baad key fuqaha mein sey bhi aksar ehle-ilm maslan Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai ke jab dono khatnon key maqam aapas mein chhu jaeyn to ghusl wajib ho gaya."
110,"sirf mani (nikalney) par ghusl wajib hota hai, ye rukhsat (chhoot) ibtadaaey (shuruaati) Islam mein thi, phir is-sey rok diya gaya."
111,"Zohri sey usi jaisi hadees riwayat hui hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- sirf mani nikalney hi ki surat mein ghusl wajib hota hai, ye hukm ibtadaaey (shuriaati) Islam mein tha, baad mein ye hukm mansookh (radd) ho gaya. 3- isi tarah Sahaba kiram mein sey kaee logon sey jin mein Ubai-bin Kaab aur Raafey bin khadij Raziallahu anhuma bhi shamil hain riwayet hui hai. 4- aur isi par aksar ehle-ilm (aalimon) ka amal hai, ke jab aadmi apni biwi ki (sharmgaah) mein jima karey to dono (miyan biwi) par ghusl wajib ho jaeyga haalanki un dono ko inzaal (sakhlan) na huwa ho."
112,"mani nikalney sey hi ghusl wajib hota hai, ka talluq ehtilaam (sawapndosh) sey hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Usman bin Affaan , Ali bin Abi Talib , Zuber , Talha , Abu-Ayyub aur Abu-Saeed (Raziallauh anhum) ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey marfooan (seedhey taur par) riwayat ki hai ke aap ney farmaya mani nikalney hi par ghusl wajib hota hai."
113,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey us shakhs key barey mein puchha gaya jo tari dekhey lekin usey ehtilaam (sawapndosh) yad na aaye, aap ney farmaya : ''woh ghusl karey'' aur us shakhs key barey mein (poochha gaya) jisey ye yad ho ke usey ehtilaam huwa hai lekin wo tari na paey to aap ney farmaya : ''uspar ghusl nahin'' Umme-Salma ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya aurat par bhi jo aisa dekhey ghusl hai? aap ney farmaya : aurten bhi (sharae ehkam mein) mardon hi ki tarah hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha ki hadees ko jis mein hai ke aadmi tari dekhey aur usey ehtilaam (sawapndosh) yaad na aaye sirf Abdullah ibne-Umar Umri hi ney Ubedullah sey riwayat kiya hai aur Abdullah bin umr Umri ki Yahya bin Saeed ney hadees key silsiley mein unkey hifz key talluq sey tazeef ki hai (zaeef thehraya hai). 2- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey kaee ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai ke jab aadmi jaagey aur tari dekhey to ghusl karey. yehi Sufiyan Sory aur Ahmed ka bhi qol hai. Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke is par ghusl us waqt wajib hoga jab wo tari nutfey ki tari ho, ye Shafai aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. aur jab wo ehtilaam (sawapndosh) dekhey aur tari na paey to aksar ehle-ilm key nazdik uspar ghusl nahin."
114,"mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey mazi key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : ''mazii sey wuzu hai aur mani sey ghusl.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Miqdaad bin Aswad aur Ubai-bin Kaab Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaee sanadon sey marfooan marvi hai ke ''mazi sey wuzu hai, aur mani sey ghusl.'' 4- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai, aur Sufiyan , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain."
115,"mujhey mazi ki wajeh sey pareshani aur takleef sey do-chaar hona padta tha. main iski wajeh sey kasrat sey ghusl kiya karta tha. mainey iska zikr Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey kiya aur is silsiley mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : ''uskey liye tumhen wuzu kafi hai.''  mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! agar wo kapdey mein lag jaey to kya karun? aap ney farmaya : to eik chullo pani ley aur usey kapdey par jahan jahan dekhey ke wo lagi hai chhidak ley ye tumharey liye kafi ho ga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- hum mazi key silsile mein is tarah ki riwayat Muhammad bin Is-haq key tareeqe sey hi jantey hain. 3- kapdey mein mazi lag janey key silsile mein ehle-ilm mein ikhtilaf hai. baaz ka qol hai ke dhona zaroori hai, yehi Shafai aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. aur baaz is baat key qaail hain ke pani chhidak lena kafi ho ga. Imam Ahmed kehtey hain : mujhey ummid hai ke pani chhidak lena kafi hoga."
116,"Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key yahan eik mehman aaya to unhoney usey (odhney key liye) usey eik zard chadar deney ka hukm diya. wo is mein soyaa to usey ehtilaam (sawapndosh) ho gaya. aisey hi bhejney mein ke usmein ehtilaam (sawapndosh) ka asar hai usey sharam mehsus hui. chunanche usney usey pani sey dho kar bheja. to Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : usney hamara kapda kyon kharab kar diya? usey apni ungliyon sey khurch deta, bas itna kafi tha. kabhi-kabhi main apni ungliyon sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key kapdey sey usey khurch deti thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram , Tabe-een aur unkey baad key fuqaha mein sey Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai ke kapdey par mani padhi. lag jaey to usey khurch dena kafi hai, haalanke dhoya na jaey."
117,"unhon-ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key kapdey sey mani dhoi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- aur Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees ''ke unhon-ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key kapdey sey mani dhoi'' unki khurachney wali hadees key khilaaf nahin hai 3۔ isliye ke khurachna kafi hai. lekin mard key liye yehi pasand kiya jata hai ke uskey kapdey par uska koi asar dikhai na dey. (kyonkey mard ko aadmiyon ki majlison mein bethna hota hai) ibne-Abbas kehtey hain : mani naak key gaadhey pani ki tarah hai, lihaza tum usey apney sey saaf kar lo chahey izkhir (ghaas) hi sey ho."
118,Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sotey aur pani ko haath na lagatey aur aap junbi (sambhog ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mei aadmi) hotey.
119,"Abu-Is'haaq sey isi tarah riwayet hui hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- yehi Saeed bin Musaiyab waghera ka qol hai. 2- kaee sanadon sey Aaisha sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) soney sey pehley wuzu kartey they. 3- ye Abu-Is'haq Sabeei ki hadees (raqam 118) sey jisey unhon-ney Aswad sey riwayat kiya hai ziyada sahih hai, aur Abu-Is'haq Sabeei sey ye hadees Shoba, Sory aur deegar kaee logon ney bhi riwayat ki hai aur unkey khayal mein ismein ghalati Abu-Is'haq Sabeei sey hui hai."
120,"unhon-ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey sawal kiya : kya hum mein sey koi janabat (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat) ki haalat mein so sakta hai? aap ney farmaya : ''haan, jab wo wuzu kar ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ammar , Aaisha , Jabir , abu-Saeed aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- umr (Raziallahu anhu) wali hadees is baab mein sab sey umda aur sahih hai. 3- yehi qol Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key as-haab aur Tabe-een mein sey bahut sey logon ka hai aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain ke jab junbi (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein aadmi) soney ka irada karey to wo soney sey pehley wuzu kar ley."
121,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unsey miley aur wo junbi (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein aadmi) they, wo kehtey hain : to main aankh bacha kar nikal gaya aur ja kar mainey ghusl kiya phir khidmat mein aaya to aap ney puchha : tum kahan they? ya : kahan chaley gaey they (Raavi ko shak hai). mainey arz kiya : main junbi (sambhog ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mei aadmi) tha. aap ney farmaya : musalman kabhi naapaak nahin hota. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Huzefa aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur unkey qol « فانخنست » key maana «تنحیت عنہ» key hain'' yani main nazar bacha kar nikal gaya.''  4- bahut sey ehle-ilm ney junbi (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein aadmi) sey musaafe ki ijazat di hai aur kaha hai ke junbi (sambhog ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mei aadmi) aur haaiza key paseeney mein koi harj nahin."
122,"Umme Sulaim binte Milhaan Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key paas aayin aur kehney lagin : Allah key Rasool ! Allah haq sey nahin sharmata padhi. kya aurat par bhi ghusl hai, jab wo khuwab mein wohi chiz dekhey jo mard dekhta hai padhi. aap ney farmaya : ''haan, jab wo mani dekhey to ghusl karey'' padhi. Umme-Salma kehti hain : mainey Umme Salaim sey kaha : Umme Salaim ! aap ney to aurton ko ruswa kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- beshtar fuqaha ka qol hai ke aurat jab khuwab mein wohi chiz dekhey jo mard dekhta hai phir usey inzaal (sakhlan) ho jaey (yani mani nikal jaey) to uspar ghusl wajib hai. yehi Sufiyan Sory aur Shafai bhi kehtey hain. 3- 2- is bab mein Umme Sulaim , Khaula , Aaisha aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
123,"kabhi-kabhi Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) janabat (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat) ka ghusl farmatey phir aa kar mujh sey garmi hasil kartey to main aap ko chimta leti, aur main baghair ghusl key hoti thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad mein koi shubh nahin. 2- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey bahut sey ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai ke mard jab ghusl kar ley to apni biwi sey chimat kar garmi hasil karney mein usey koi muzaaeqa (harj) nahin. wo aurat key ghusl karney sey pehley uskey sath (chimat-kar) so sakta hai. Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain."
124,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''pak mitti musalman ko pak karney wali hai haalanke wo das-saal tak pani na paaey, phir jab wo pani paa ley to usey apni khaal (yani jism) par bahaaey, yehi uskey liye behtar hai.'' Mehmood (Mehmood bin Ghailaan) ney apni riwayat mein yun kaha hai : pak mitti musalman ka wuzu hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin Amr aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aksar fuqaha ka qol yehi hai ke junbi (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein aadmi) ya haaiza jab pani na paaeyn to tayammum kar key namaz padhein. 4- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) junbi (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein aadmi) key liye tayammum durust nahin samajhtey they agar-che wo pani na paaey. unsey ye bhi marvi hai ke unhon-ney apney qol sey ruju kar liya tha aur ye kaha tha ke wo jab pani nahin paaeyga, tayammum kareyga, yehi Sufiyan Sory , Malik , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain."
125,"Faatima binte Abi Habish (Raziallahu Anha) ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key paas aa-kar kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main aisi aurat hun ke mujhey istihaza ka khoon padhi. aata hai to main pak hi nahin reh paati, kya main namaz chhod dun? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin, ye to eik rag hai haiz nahin hai, jab haiz aaye to namaz chhod do aur jab wo chala jaey (yani haiz key din purey ho jaeyn) to khoon dho kar (ghusl kar key) namaz padho.''  Abu-Muaawiya ki riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''har namaz key liye wuzu karo yahan tak ke wo waqt (haiz ka waqt) aa jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein bahut sey ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai, aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , Malik , ibne-Mubarak aur Shafai bhi yehi kehtey hain ke jab haayzaa aurat key haiz key din guzar jaeyn to wo ghusl karey aur har namaz key liye (taza) wuzu karey."
126,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney mustahaza key silsiley mein farmaya : ''woh un dino mein jin mein usey haiz aata ho namaz chhodey rahey, phir wo ghusl kerey. aur (istihaaze ka khoon aaney par) har namaz key liye wuzu kerey. roza rakhey aur namaz padhey ''."
127,Shurek ney isi mafhoom key sath isi tarah ki hadees bayan ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees mein Shurek Abul-Yuqzaan sey riwayat karney mein munfarid (alag) hain. 2- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya haayza aurat key barey mein kehtey hain ke agar wo har namaz key waqt ghusl karey to ye uskey liye ziyada ehtiyat ki baat hai aur agar wo har namaz key liye wuzu karey to ye uskey liye kafi hai aur agar wo eik ghusl sey do namazein jama karey to bhi kafi hai.
128,"Main sakht qisam key istihaza mein mubtala rehti thi, main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein masla poochhney aur aap ko uski khabar deney key liye hazir hui, mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apni behan Zenab binte Hajash key ghar paya to arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main sakht qisam key istihaza mein mubtala rehti hun, is silsile mein aap mujhey kya hukm detey hain, isney to mujhey saum aur namaz dono sey rok diya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''main tujhey rui rakhney ka hukm dey raha hun us-sey khoon band ho jaeyga.'' unhon-ney arz kiya : wo is-sey ziyada hai (rui rakhney sey nahin rukeyga) aap ney farmaya : ''to langot baandh liya karo.''  kaha : khoon us-sey bhi ziyada aa raha hai, to aap ney farmaya : ''tum langot key nichey eik kapda rakh liya karo.''  kaha : ye us sey bhi ziyada hai, mujhey bahut tezi sey khoon behta hai, to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''to main tujhey do baaton ka hukm deta hun un dono mein sey tum jo bhi kar lo tumharey liye kafi hoga aur agar tum dono par qudrat rakh sako to tum ziyada behtar jaanti ho.''  aapney farmaya : ''ye to sirf shetan ki chot (maar) hai to chhe ya saat din jo Allah key ilm mein hain unhen to haiz key shumar kar phir ghusl kar ley aur jab to samajh ley ke Tu Pak aur saaf ho gaee ho to chobis ya teyiees din namaz padh aur rozey rakh. ye tumharey liye kafi hai, aur isi tarah karti raho jaisa ke haiz wali aurten karti hain : haiz key oqaat mein haaiza aur paki key waqton mein pak rehti hain, aur agar tum is baat par qadir ho ke Zohar ko kuchh der sey padho aur Asr ko qadrey jaldi padh lo to ghusl kar key pak saaf ho ja aur Zohar aur Asr ko eik sath padh liya karo, phir maghrib ko zara der kar key aur Isha ko kuchh pehley kar key phir ghusl kar key ye dono namazein eik sath padh ley to aisa kar liya karo, aur subah key liye alag ghusl kar key Fajr padho. agar tum qadir ho to is tarah karo aur rozey rakho.'' phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''in dono baaton padhi. mein sey ye dusri surat padhi. mujhey ziyada pasand hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney is hadees ko Hasan sahih kaha hai aur isi tarah Ahmed bin Hanbal ney bhi kaha hai ke ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 3- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya haaiza aurat key barey mein kehtey hain ke aurat jab apney haiz key aaney aur janey ko jaanti ho, aur aana ye hai ke khoon kaalaa ho aur jana ye hai ke wo zardi mein badal jaey to uska hukm Fatima bin Abi Habish (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees key mutabiq hoga padhi. aur agar haayza aurat key liye istihaza sey pehley (haiz key) dinon (din) maroof hain to wo apney haiz key dino mein namaz chhod deygi phir ghusl kareygi aur har namaz key liye wuzu kareygi. aur jab khoon jari rahey aur (haiz key) dinon malum na hon aur na hi wo haiz key aaney janey ko jaanti ho to uska hukm Hamna binte Jahash (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees key mutabiq hoga 4- isi tarah Abu Ubaid ney kaha hai. Shafai kehtey hain : jab haayza aurat ko pehli baar jab usney khoon dekha tabhi sey barabar khoon jari rahey to wo khoon shuru honey sey ley kar pandarah din tak namaz chhodey raheygi, phir agar wo pandarah din mein ya us-sey pehley pak ho jati hai to goya yehi uskey haiz key din hain aur agar wo pandarah din sey ziyada khoon dekhey, to wo chaudah din ki namaz qaza kereygi aur uskey baad aurton key haiz ki muddat jo eik din aur eik raat hai, ki namaz chhod deygi. 4- haiz ki kam sey kam muddat aur sab sey ziyada muddat mein ehle-ilm key darmiyan ikhtilaf hai, baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : haiz ki sab sey kam muddat teen din aur sab sey ziyada muddat das din hai, yehi Sufiyan Sory , aur ehle-koofa ka qol hai aur isi ko ibne-Mubarak bhi ikhtiyar kartey hain. unsey iskey khilaf bhi riwayat hua hai. baaz ehle-ilm jin-mein Ata bin Abi Ribah bhi hain, kehtey hain ke haiz ki kam sey kam muddat eik din aur eik raat hai aur iski ziyada sey ziyada muddat pandarah din hai, aur yehi Malik , Auzaai , Shafai , Ahmed , Is-haq bin Raahviya aur Abu Ubaid ka qol hai."
129,"Umme-Habiba binte Hajash ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey masla puchha aur kaha ke mujhey istihaza ka khoon aata hai aur main pak nahin reh paati hun. to kya main namaz chhod dun? aap ney farmaya : nahin, ye to mehaz eik rag hai, lihaza tum ghusl karo phir namaz padho.''  to wo har namaz key liye ghusl karti thin. ibne Shahab Zohri ney is-ka zikr nahin kiya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu Anha) ko har namaz key waqt ghusl karney ka hukm diya, balke ye aisa amal tha jisey wo apney tor par kiya karti thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- isi ke saath ye hadees Zohri sey (an Umra an Aaisha) key tareeqe sey bhi riwayat ki jati hai ke Umme-Habiba binte Jahash ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey masla poochha.  2- baaz ehle-ilm (aalimon) ney kaha hai ke haayza aurat har namaz key waqt ghusl kareygi."
130,eik aurat ney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey puchha : kya hum haiz key dino wali namaz ki qaza kiya karen? to unhon-ney kaha : kya to harooriya padhi. hai? hum mein sey eik ko haiz aata tha to usey qaza ka hukm nahin diya jata tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur Aaisha sey aur kaee sanadon sey bhi marvi hai ke haaiza namaz qaza nahin kareygi.  3- aksar fuqaha ka yehi qol hai. unkey darmiyan koi ikhtilaf nahin ke haaiza roza qaza kareygi aur namaz qaza nahin kareygi.
131,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''haaiza aur junbi (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein aadmi) Quran sey kuchh na padhein.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees ko ham sirf Ismail bin Ayash hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain. jis mein ibne-Umar sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''junbi (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein aadmi) aur haaiza (Quran) na padhein.''  3- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey aksar ehle-ilm aur unkey baad key log maslan Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai ke haaiza aur junbi (shohar biwi ke darmiyan ham-bistari ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein aadmi) aayat key kisi tukdey ya eik-aadh harf key siwa Quran sey kuchh na padhein. haan un logon ney junbi (sambhog ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mei aadmi) aur haaiza ko tasbih aur tahleel ki ijazat di hai."
132,"mujhey jab haiz aata to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey teh-band baandhney ka hukm detey phir mujhsey chimat'te aur boss aur kinaar kartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. Sahaba kiram o Tabe-een mein sey bahut sey ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai aur yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain. 2-is bab mein Umme-Salma aur Memuna Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
133,mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey haaiza key sath khaney key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : ''uskey sath khaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Saad Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha aur Anas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai : ye log haaiza key sath khaney mein koi harj nahin jantey. albatta uskey wuzu key bachey huye pani key silsile mein unmein ikhtilaf hai. baaz logon ney uski ijazat di hai aur baaz ney uski tahaarat (paakizgi) sey bachey huye pani ko makrooh kaha hai.
134,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : ''masjid sey mujhey boriya utha kar do.'' to mainey arz kiya : main haaiza hun, aap ney farmaya : ''tera haiz terey haath mein nahin hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai. hum is masle mein ke ''haaiza key masjid sey koi chiz uthaney mein koi harj nahin'' unkey darmiyan koi ikhtilaf nahin jantey."
135,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''jo kisi haaiza key paas aaya yani us-sey jima (sambhog) kiya ya kisi aurat key paas peechhey key raastey sey aaya, ya kisi kaahin key paas (ghaib ka haal jaan-ney key liye) aaya to usney un chizon ka inkar kiya jo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( par nazil ki gaee hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ehle-ilm key nazdik Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key us farman ka matlab taghleez hai, Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey ye bhi marvi hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''jisney kisi haaiza sey sohbat ki to wo eik Dinar sadqa karey, agar haaiza sey sohbat ka irtikab kufr hota to is mein kaffaarey ka hukm na diya jata.'' 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney is hadees ko sanad ke aitibar sey zaeef qarar diya hai."
136,Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney us aadmi key barey mein jo apni biwi sey haiz ki haalat mein jima karta hai farmaya : '' wo aadha Dinar sadqa karey ''.
137,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jab khoon surkh ho (aur jima kar ley to) eik Dinar aur jab zard ho to aadha Dinar ( sadqa karey ( ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- haaiza sey jima key kaffaarey ki hadees ibne-Abbas sey moqufan aur marfooan dono tarah sey marvi hai, 2- aur baaz ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain. ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain : ye apney rab sey istighfar kerega, is par koi kaffara nahin, ibne-Mubarak key qol ki tarah baaz Tabe-een sey bhi marvi hai jin mein Saeed bin Juber , Ibrahim Nakhai bhi shamil hain. aur aksar Misri ulama ka yehi qol hai."
138,"eik aurat ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey us kapdey key barey mein puchha jis mein haiz ka khoon lag jaey, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' usey khurch do , phir usey pani sey mal do , phir is par pani baha do aur is mein namaz padho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- khoon key dhoney key silsiley mein Asma (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur Umme-Qais bint Mohsin Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- kapdey mein jo khoon lag jaey aur usey dhoney sey pehley is mein namaz padh ley… uskey barey mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai; Tabe-een mein sey baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke jab khoon dirham ki miqdaar mein ho aur dhoey baghair namaz padh ley to namaz dohraaey, aur baaz kehtey hain ke jab khoon dirham ki miqdaar sey ziyada ho to namaz dohraaey warna nahin, yehi Sufiyan Sory aur ibne-Mubarak ka qol hai padhi. aur Tabe-een waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ney namaz key dohraaney ko wajib nahin kaha hai bhaley hi khoon dirham ki miqdaar sey ziyada ho, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya yehi kehtey hain padhi. , jabke Shafai kehtey hain ke is par dhona wajib hai bhale hi dirham ki miqdaar sey kam ho, is silsiley mein unhoney sakhti barti hai۔"
139,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key zamaney mein nifaas wali aurten chaalis din tak bethi rehti thin, aur jhaiyon key sabab hum apney chehron par waras ( naami ghaas hai) malti thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, isey hum sirf abu-Sehal hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- Sahaba kiraam, Tabe-een aur unkey baad key logon mein sey tamam ehle-ilm ka is baat par ijmaa hai ke nifaas wali aurten chaalis din tak namaz nahin padhengi۔ albatta agar wo is sey pehley pak ho lein to ghusl karkey namaz padhney lag jaeyn, agar chaalis din key baad bhi wo khoon dekhen to aksar ehle-ilm ka kehna hai ke chaalis din key baad wo namaz na choden, yehi aksar fuqaha ka qol hai. Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain. Hasan Basri kehtey hain ke pachas din tak namaz chhodey rahey jab wo paki na dekhey, Ata bin abi Ribah aur Shaaby sey saath din tak marvi hai."
140,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eik hi ghusl mein sabhi biwiyon ka chakkar laga letey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- bahut sey ehle-ilm ka jin mein Hasan Basri bhi shamil hain yehi qol hai ke wuzu karney sey pehley dobara jima karney mein koi harj nahin ."
141,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi apni biwi sey sohbat karey phir wo dobara sohbat karna chahey to un dono key darmiyan wuzu kar ley '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat aai hai, 2- abu-Saeed ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 3- umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ka qol hai, ehle-ilm mein sey bahut sey logon ney yehi kaha hai ke jab aadmi apni biwi sey jima karey phir dobara jima karna chahey to jima sey pehley dobara wuzu kerey."
142,"Abdullah bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) apni qom key Imam they, namaz khadi hui to unhoney eik shakhs ka haath pakad kar usey ( imaamat key liye ( aagey badha diya aur kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : '' jab namaz key liye iqaamat ho chuki ho aur tum mein sey koi qazaey-hajat ki zarurat mehsus karey to wo pehley qazaey-hajat key liye jaey ''."
143,"mainey ummul-momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) sey kaha : main lamba daman rakhney wali aurat hun aur mera gandi jagahon par bhi chalna hota hai, ( to main kya karun ? ( unhoney kaha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya hai : '' uskey baad ki) pak ( zamin usey pak kar deti hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai ke hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key sath gandi jagahon par sey guzarney key baad paaon nahin dhotey they, 2- ehle-ilm mein sey bahut sey logon ka yehi qol hai ke jab aadmi kisi gandey raastey sey ho kar aaye to usey paaon dhoney zaroori nahin siwaye uskey ke gandagi geeli ho to aisi surat mein jo kuch laga hai usey dho ley ."
144,"Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney unhen chehrey aur dono hatheliyon key tayammum ka hukm diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- yehi Sahaba kiram mein sey kaee ehle-ilm ka qol hai jin mein Ali , Ammar , ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) shamil hain aur Tabe-een mein sey bhi kaee logon ka hai jin mein Shaaby, Ata aur makhool bhi hain, un sab ka kehna hai ke tayammum chehrey aur dono hatheliyon key liye eik hi baar maarna hai, usi key qaail Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi hain, 4- baaz ehle-ilm jin mein ibne-Umar , Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) , Ibrahim Nakhai aur Hasan Basri shamil hain kehtey hain ke tayammum chehra key liye eik zarba aur dono haathon key liye kohniyon tak eik zarba hai, uskey qaail Sufiyan Sory, Malik, ibne-Mubarak aur Shafai hain, 5- tayammum key silsiley mein Ammar sey ye hadees jis mein chehrey aur dono hatheliyon key liye eik zarba ka zikr hai aur bhi kaee sanadon sey marvi hai, 6- Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) sey tayammum ki hadees mein naqal kya gaya hai ke hamney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key sath shaanon aur baghlon tak tayammum kya. 7- baaz ehle-ilm ney tayammum key silsiley mein Ammar key chehrey aur dono hatheliyon wali hadees ki tazeef ki hai kyonkey un sey shaanon aur baghlon wali hadees bhi marvi hai, 8- Is-haq bin Ibrahim Mukhlid Hanzali (ibne-Raahviya ( kehtey hain ke chehra aur dono kohniyon key liye eik hi zarba wali tayammum key silsiley ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 9- Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees jis mein hai ke hamney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key sath shaanon aur baghlon tak tayammum kya chehrey aur dono hatheliyon wali hadees key mukhalif nahin kyonkey Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye zikr nahin kya hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney hamen uska hukm diya tha balke unhoney sirf itna kaha hai ke hamney aisa aisa kya, phir jab unhoney us barey mein Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sey puchha to aap ney unhen sirf chehrey aur dono ka hukm diya, to wo chehrey aur dono hatheliyon hi par ruk gaey. jiski Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney unhen taalim di, uski daleel tayammum key silsila ka Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ka wo fatwa hai jisey unhoney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) key baad diya hai ke tayammum sirf chehrey aur dono hatheliyon hi ka hai, is mein is baat par dalalat hai ke wo usi jagah ruk gaey jiski Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney unhen taalim di padhi. aur aap ney unhen jo taalim di thi wo chehrey aur dono hatheliyon tak hi mehdud thi."
145,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey tayammum key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : Allah Taala ney apni kitab mein jis waqt wuzu ka zikr kya to farmaya '' apney chehrey ko aur apney haathon ko kohniyon tak dhoo'' , aur tayammum key barey mein farmaya : '' apney chehron aur haathon par masah karo '' , aur farmaya : '' chori karney waley mard o aurat ki saza ye hai ke unkey haath kaat do '' to haath kaatney key silsiley mein sunnat ye thi ke) pahunchey tak) hatheli kaati jati, lihaza tayammum sirf chehrey aur hatheliyon hi tak hoga . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
146,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamen Quran padhatey they. chahey koi bhi haalat ho jab tak ke aap junbi na hotey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Sahaba kiram aur Tabe-een mein sey kaee ehle-ilm ka yehi qol hai ke aadmi wuzu key baghair Quran padh sakta hai, lekin musahaf mein dekh kar usi waqt padhey jab wo baa-wuzoo ho. Sufiyan Sory, Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai."
147,"eik ea'rabi masjid mein dakhil huwa, Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bethey huye they, usney namaz padhi, jab namaz padh chuka to kaha : aey Allah to mujh par aur Muhammad par reham farma aur hamarey sath kisi aur par reham mat farma. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney uski taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : ''tum ney eik kushada chiz (yani rehmat Ilaahi) ko tang kar diya'', phir abhi thodi hi der hui thi ke wo masjid mein ja kar peshab karney laga, log tezi sey uski taraf badhey, to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ney farmaya : ''us par eik dol pani baha do, phir aap ney farmaya : ''tum to aasani karney waley bana kar bhejey gaey ho na ke sakhti karney waley '' padhi. ."
148,"isi tarah ki hadees marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood, ibne-Abbas aur Waasila Isqa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
